scripts.comment: 我们已预设背景在“停止”时重置 否则，用户需要手动更改或重新加载背景以清除剪切/粘贴效果 We had preset the background to reset when "Stopped" Otherwise, user will need to manually change or reload the background to clear the cut/paste effect
